# Deploying Agents to Hostinger VPS

[ ] Locate the local agent source code
[ ] Determine the deployment method (SSH/SCP, Git, Docker, etc.)
[ ] Connect to Hostinger VPS via SSH
[ ] Install necessary dependencies on VPS (Node.js, PM2, etc.)
[ ] Transfer the code or clone the repository to the VPS
[ ] Configure environment variables (.env) on the VPS
[ ] Start and configure the agents to run 24/7 (e.g., via PM2 or a systemd service)
[ ] Verify the agents are fully operational via Telegram
